Pytanie [PPL(A)] 1073: Kiedy aktualizujemy depeszę TAF TEMPO?
Odpowiedź: Co najmniej na godzinę przed.
źródło
TEMPORARY Group: ie. (TEMPO 1316)
The TEMPO group is used for any conditions in wind, visibility, weather, or sky condition which are expected
to last for generally less than an hour at a time (occasional), and are expected to occur during less than half
the time period. The TEMPO indicator is followed by a four-digit group giving the beginning hour and ending
hour of the time period during which the temporary conditions are expected. Only the changing forecast
meteorological conditions are included in TEMPO groups. The omitted conditions are carried over from the
previous time group.
